linux内核启动时会加载fbtft驱动，注册framebuffer设备，打印如下信息：

    [    1.131698] fbtft_of_value: buswidth = 8
    [    1.135680] fbtft_of_value: debug = 0
    [    1.139345] fbtft_of_value: rotate = 270
    [    1.143268] fbtft_of_value: fps = 30
